products.title: Turin 25mm Shimmer Pearl White Perfect Fit Venetian Blind
products.description: The metallic range offers the best urban and contemporary feel of the metallic blind that will add a character to any space. Add something different to the style of any room with their metallic 25mm pearl venetian blind. This blind is ideal with neutral colour schemes.
